</entry><entry thead="no"><para>1.0</para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
<para><heading level="2">Example </heading>
</para>
<para>To see how to use this interface in a C++ application, refer to the <ref refid="cpp_sample__work_with_a_d_l" kindref="compound">WorkWithADL C++ sample</ref>.<linebreak/>
 For a C application, refer to the <ref refid="c_sample__work_with_a_d_l" kindref="compound">WorkWithADL C sample</ref>.</para>
